{
  "id": "securityclaw-intro",
  "title": "SecurityClaw: Autonomous SOC Agent",
  "description": "A guided tour of SecurityClaw's architecture — an autonomous Security Operations Center agent that monitors OpenSearch data, builds RAG behavioral baselines, and uses local Ollama LLMs for threat analysis.",
