      "title": "Core Framework",
      "description": "The core/ directory is the engine room. The Runner orchestrates skill discovery and scheduling. Config loads YAML + env overrides. Memory provides bounded JSON working storage for findings, decisions, and escalations. The DB connector abstracts OpenSearch/Elasticsearch, and the LLM provider wraps Ollama for chat and embeddings.",
