      "id": "chat-router-deep-dive",
      "title": "Chat Router: The Supervisor Brain",
      "description": "The chat_router is the largest and most sophisticated skill. It acts as a conversational supervisor that routes user queries to the right skill, manages multi-turn reasoning with chain-of-thought prompts, and synthesizes results. Its prompt engineering is split across dedicated markdown files for routing, strategy, evaluation, and reflection.",
