    {
      "id": "threat-pipeline",
      "title": "Threat Detection Pipeline",
      "description": "The security pipeline flows through three stages. First, network_baseliner builds RAG embeddings of normal behavior every 6 hours. Next, anomaly_triage polls for findings every minute and enriches them with LLM analysis. Finally, threat_analyst delivers a verdict — TRUE_THREAT or FALSE_POSITIVE — using RAG context and external intelligence from AbuseIPDB, AlienVault, VirusTotal, and Talos.",
